WEBVTT

NOTE D. P. Gumby demonstrates flower arranging, badly

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
[caption] FLOWER ARRANGEMENT

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.000
[action] Pull back to studio: piles of flowers on a table.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:05.500
[caption] INTRODUCED BY D. P. GUMBY

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:14.000
<v Gumby>
Good evening. First take a bunch of flowers. [action] Grabs flowers. Pretty begonias, irises, freesias and cry-manthesums… then arrange them nicely in a vase. [action] He jams flowers head-down into vase, stuffing wildly; bangs with a mallet. Get in! Get in! Get in!

